          { "feature": "most_severe_metabolic_profile", "weight": 4 }
        ],
        "management": "Lifestyle modification (diet, exercise, weight loss). COCP for cycle regulation and anti-androgen effect. Metformin if insulin resistance. Anti-androgens (spironolactone) for hirsutism."
